      </subsection>

      <subsection name="Examples" id="IllegalSymbol_Examples">
        <p id="Example1-config">
          To configure the check:
        </p>
        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-xml">
&lt;module name="Checker"&gt;
  &lt;module name="TreeWalker"&gt;
    &lt;module name="IllegalSymbol"/&gt;
  &lt;/module&gt;
&lt;/module&gt;
</code></pre></div>
        <p id="Example1-code">
          Example:
        </p>
        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-java">
public class Example1 {
  // âœ… Enhancement completed
  // ðŸ˜€ Happy coding
  int value = 1;
}
</code></pre></div><hr class="example-separator"/>
        <p id="Example2-config">
          To configure the check to forbid emoji ranges:
        </p>
        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-xml">
&lt;module name="Checker"&gt;
  &lt;module name="TreeWalker"&gt;
    &lt;module name="IllegalSymbol"&gt;
      &lt;property name="symbolCodes" value="0x1F300-0x1F5FF,  0x1F680-0x1F6FF"/&gt;
    &lt;/module&gt;
  &lt;/module&gt;
&lt;/module&gt;
</code></pre></div>
        <p id="Example2-code">
            Example:
        </p>
        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-java">
public class Example2 {
  int x = 1;

  // ðŸŒŸ Star // violation 'Illegal Unicode symbol detected'
  int star = 3;

  // ðŸš€ Rocket // violation 'Illegal Unicode symbol detected'
  int fast = 3;
}
</code></pre></div><hr class="example-separator"/>
        <p id="Example3-config">
          To configure the check for ASCII-only mode:
        </p>
        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-xml">
&lt;module name="Checker"&gt;
  &lt;module name="TreeWalker"&gt;
    &lt;module name="IllegalSymbol"&gt;
      &lt;property name="asciiOnly" value="true"/&gt;
    &lt;/module&gt;
  &lt;/module&gt;
&lt;/module&gt;
</code></pre></div>
        <p id="Example3-code">
            Example:
